Package org.osgi.service.jakartars.runtime.dto

Class DTOConstants

java.lang.Object
org.osgi.service.jakartars.runtime.dto.DTOConstants
public final class DTOConstants extends Object
Defines standard constants for the DTOs. The error codes are defined to take the same values as used by the Http Service Whiteboard
